\c 47
\s Marudzi ose ngaarumbidze Jehovha
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora.
\p
\v 1 Uchirai, imi vanhu vose! Pururudzai kuna Mwari nezwi romufaro mukuru!
\v 2 Nokuti Jehovha wokumusoro-soro anotyisa; Ndiye Mambo mukuru panyika yose.
\v 3 Ndiye anotikundisa ndudzi dzavanhu,
\s Nendudzi pasi petsoka dzedu.
\p
\v 4 Ndiye anotitsaurira nhaka yedu, Iyo pfuma yaJakobho waanoda.
\p
\v 5 Mwari akwira nokudanidzira, Jehovha nokurira kwehwamanda.
\p
\v 6 Imbirai Mwari nziyo dzokurumbidza,
\s muimbirei nziyo dzokurumbidza; Imbirai Mambo wedu nziyo dzokurumbidza,
\s muimbirei nziyo dzokurumbidza.
\p
\v 7 Nokuti Mwari ndiye Mambo wapasi pose;
\s Muimbirei rwiyo rwakanaka rwokumurumbidza.
\s Mwari anobata ushe hwavahedheni; Mwari agere pachigaro chake chitsvene choushe.
\p
\v 9 Machinda avanhu aungana pamwechete navanhu vaMwari waAbhurahamu; Nokuti nhoo dzapasi pose ndedzaMwari;
\s Ndiye mukuru-kuru kwazvo.
